        <a href="https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apache License 2.0</a>.
        The source code is available on
        <a href="https://github.com/meysam81/hackernew" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        You are free to use, modify, and distribute the code in accordance with the license terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Content Disclaimer</h2>
