        and
        <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/newsguidelines.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">guidelines</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>No Warranty</h2>
      <p>
        This service is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied.
        The maintainers of HackerNew make no guarantees regarding:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Availability or uptime of the service</li>
        <li>Accuracy or completeness of displayed content</li>
        <li>Fitness for any particular purpose</li>
        <li>Security of user data (though we take reasonable precautions)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

