      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        The HackerNew project maintainers shall not be liable for any damages arising from
        the use or inability to use this service, including but not limited to direct,
        indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>When using HackerNew, you agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Attempt to disrupt or overload the service</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to scrape content excessively</li>
        <li>Circumvent any security measures</li>
        <li>Use the service for any illegal purpose</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Accounts</h2>
      <p>
        Account creation is optional. If you choose to create an account via GitHub or Google
        authentication, you are responsible for maintaining the security of your account.
      </p>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to terminate accounts that violate these terms or abuse the service.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes
        constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about these terms, please open an issue on our
        <a href="https://github.com/meysam81/hackernew/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub repository</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-2);
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-3);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-3);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-3);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-6);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
